                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "« Sacrebleu ! voilà le soleil,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Dit l'oiseau dont la plume pousse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Il va sécher l'herbe et la mousse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Et nous faire un monde vermeil :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Il fait tout, ce roi sans pareil.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Sacrebleu, voilà le soleil !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Sacrebleu ! voilà le soleil,\nDit l'oiseau dont la plume pousse,\nIl va sécher l'herbe et la mousse,\nEt nous faire un monde vermeil :\nIl fait tout, ce roi sans pareil.\nSacrebleu, voilà le soleil !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Je voudrais vivre cent mille ans,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "S'il avait cent mille ans à vivre.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Pour le regarder et le suivre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Suspendu sur les blés brûlans,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Quand même il pleuvrait des milans.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Je voudrais vivre cent mille ans !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je voudrais vivre cent mille ans,\nS'il avait cent mille ans à vivre.\nPour le regarder et le suivre,\nSuspendu sur les blés brûlans,\nQuand même il pleuvrait des milans.\nJe voudrais vivre cent mille ans !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Les milans ! qu'ils viennent un peu :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "J'en ai peur comme d'une paille ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Je m'en amuse et je m'en raille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Les pieds croisés devant mon feu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Voici le soleil, sacrebleu !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Les milans, qu'ils viennent un peu !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les milans ! qu'ils viennent un peu :\nJ'en ai peur comme d'une paille ;\nJe m'en amuse et je m'en raille,\nLes pieds croisés devant mon feu.\nVoici le soleil, sacrebleu !\nLes milans, qu'ils viennent un peu !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Bonnes gens, que cet astre est beau !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "C'est l'écusson du divin Maître :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "L'œuf ardent des âmes, peut-être,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Allumant tout comme un flambeau,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Ressuscitant larve et tombeau.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Bonnes gens ! que cet astre est beau !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Bonnes gens, que cet astre est beau !\nC'est l'écusson du divin Maître :\nL'œuf ardent des âmes, peut-être,\nAllumant tout comme un flambeau,\nRessuscitant larve et tombeau.\nBonnes gens ! que cet astre est beau !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Hardi les fleurs et les chansons !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Le printemps me monte à la tête :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "C'est Dieu qui va payer la fête !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "À vos rangs, messieurs les pinsons ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "La table est dressée aux buissons,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Hardi les fleurs et les chansons !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Hardi les fleurs et les chansons !\nLe printemps me monte à la tête :\nC'est Dieu qui va payer la fête !\nÀ vos rangs, messieurs les pinsons ;\nLa table est dressée aux buissons,\nHardi les fleurs et les chansons !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Mon habit vient d'un bon tailleur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Il est léger pour les montagnes ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Il plaît aux cités, aux campagnes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Où le peuple n'est point railleur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "L'homme n'en fait pas de meilleur :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Mon habit vient d'un bon tailleur !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mon habit vient d'un bon tailleur.\nIl est léger pour les montagnes ;\nIl plaît aux cités, aux campagnes.\nOù le peuple n'est point railleur.\nL'homme n'en fait pas de meilleur :\nMon habit vient d'un bon tailleur !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Le monde est assez grand pour moi :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Tout m'appelle au loin, tout m'avive,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Et je vais de mon aile vive,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Égayer la vitre du roi.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Je vole plus haut que-la loi :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Le monde est assez grand pour moi !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le monde est assez grand pour moi :\nTout m'appelle au loin, tout m'avive,\nEt je vais de mon aile vive,\nÉgayer la vitre du roi.\nJe vole plus haut que-la loi :\nLe monde est assez grand pour moi !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Je suis rempli d'aise et d'amour,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "J'ai cinq aurores et demie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Il me faut au moins une amie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Pour peupler un si grand séjour :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Je veux faire un nid à mon tour ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Je suis rempli d'aise et d'amour ! »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je suis rempli d'aise et d'amour,\nJ'ai cinq aurores et demie !\nIl me faut au moins une amie,\nPour peupler un si grand séjour :\nJe veux faire un nid à mon tour ;\nJe suis rempli d'aise et d'amour ! »"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Petit paysan des oiseaux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Tu dis cela quand on t'écoute",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Aux sillons de la grande route,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Ou sur la tête des roseaux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Dont les femmes font leurs fuseaux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Petit paysan des oiseaux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Petit paysan des oiseaux !\nTu dis cela quand on t'écoute\nAux sillons de la grande route,\nOu sur la tête des roseaux,\nDont les femmes font leurs fuseaux,\nPetit paysan des oiseaux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Le cœur le plus triste est charmé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "De ta joie alerte et volante.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "La mémoire y coule moins lente ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Et s'il a jamais rien aimé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Tout rêveur et tout désarmé",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Le cœur le plus triste est charmé !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le cœur le plus triste est charmé,\nDe ta joie alerte et volante.\nLa mémoire y coule moins lente ;\nEt s'il a jamais rien aimé,\nTout rêveur et tout désarmé\nLe cœur le plus triste est charmé !"
        }
